Installation instructions
-------------------------

== Requirements ==
If you find that this script works with any older versions of these 
applications, please drop me a note at and@vmn.dk.

Perl version 5.8.8 or later
Fortune (for !fortune functionality)

= Perl modules =
Net::IRC v.0.75
DBI v.1.52
DBD::SQLite v.1.12
LWP::UserAgent v.5.805

== Installation ==
1) Copy anna.db to ~/.anna/anna.db
2) Run Anna^ with `perl anna.pl`
3) ???
4) PROFIT!
Note: You may specify where anna.db is located on the command-line or in the 
file, so you don't nescessarily have to place it in ~/.anna/.
